Class ECpdsApplication.DestinationForREST

java.lang.Object
ecmwf.ecpds.master.plugin.service.ECpdsApplication.DestinationForREST
Enclosing class:
ECpdsApplication
protected static class ECpdsApplication.DestinationForREST extends Object
The Class DestinationForREST. This class is used to encapsulate the Destination class into a front end class to show only the required fields for the destination/* endpoints.
